show.description: Six years ago, Shirley was drugged and framed at her promotion party, leading to a scandal. Returning to her hometown with her illegitimate son, she seeks the truth. Working at her sister's fiancé Neil's company, she and Neil form a bond, and her son feels a strange connection to him. Shirley is determined to find out who the man was that night and unveil the truth.
